dcterms:description: Corneal confocal microscopy images of nerve fibers captured from the subbasal plexus immediately above Bowman's membrane of the cornea. The dataset includes images from 176 subjects (84 healthy and 92 patients with Type 1 diabetes) with manual annotations of nerve fibers.
dcterms:title: CCM dataset

dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset generated for quantitative evaluation of nerve fiber segmentation methods, created by applying image inpainting techniques to real CCM images and generating synthetic nerve fibers.
dcterms:title: Synthetic CCM dataset
